(define/contract (maximum-triplet-value nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let* ((max-val 0)
         (n (length nums))
         (min-prefix (make-vector n))
         (max-suffix (make-vector n)))
    (vector-set! min-prefix 0 (list-ref nums 0))
    (for ([i (in-range 1 n)])
      (vector-set! min-prefix i (min (vector-ref min-prefix (- i 1)) (list-ref nums i))))
    (vector-set! max-suffix (- n 1) (list-ref nums (- n 1)))
    (for ([i (in-range (- n 2) -1 -1)])
      (vector-set! max-suffix i (max (vector-ref max-suffix (+ i 1)) (list-ref nums i))))
    (for ([i (in-range 1 (- n 1))])
      (let* ((min-val (vector-ref min-prefix (- i 1)))
             (max-val-suffix (vector-ref max-suffix (+ i 1)))
             (current (list-ref nums i))
             (potential (* (- current min-val) max-val-suffix)))
        (when (> potential max-val)
          (set! max-val potential))))
    (if (> max-val 0) max-val 0)))
